panels.name: LDAP Calls Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code
| where function = "ADHelper"
| if(action matches "*LDAP*", "LDAP", "Total") as LDAP_usage | timeslice 10 buckets | count _timeslice, ldap_usage | transpose row _timeslice column ldap_usage

panels.name: Error Codes Summary
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify ErrorCode
| parse "ErrorCode = *," as error_code
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code | count error_code | top 10 error_code by _count

panels.name: ADHelper Action Distribution
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code
| where function = "ADHelper"
| if((action matches "*group*" or action matches "*Group*"), 1, 0) as group_action
| if((action matches "*domain*" or action matches "*Domain*"), 1, 0) as domain_action
| if((action matches "*Looking for user*" or action matches "*Validating user*" or action matches "*ValidateUserHelper*"), 1, 0) as user_action
| if((action matches "*SearchObjectByADUserDescriptor*" or action matches "*GetObjectByPath*"), 1, 0) as object_action
| sum(group_action) as group_actions, sum(domain_action) as domain_actions, sum(user_action) as user_actions, sum(object_action) as object_actions

panels.name: Top 10 Message Types
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify ADHelper
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code | count message_type | top 10 message_type by _count

panels.name: Domain Controller Usage
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code
| where function = "ADHelper"
| where action matches "*UseDomainController*"
| parse field = action "UseDomainController:*-*.AdaptivePlanning.*" as field1, domain_controller, domain_type
| fields - field1, domain_type | timeslice 10 buckets | count _timeslice, domain_controller | transpose row _timeslice column domain_controller

panels.name: Top 10 Functions
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code | count function | top 10 function by _count

panels.name: Functions Logged Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code | timeslice 10 buckets | count _timeslice, function | transpose row _timeslice column function

panels.name: Failed Logons by User Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$Centrify ValidateUserHelper (failed or Failed or exception or ERROR)
| parse "[*|(null)|(null)|*|*|*|*] *:*" as proxy_host,end_code,status_code_1,status_code_2,message_type,function,action
| fields - proxy_host, status_code_1, status_code_2, end_code
| parse field=action "Validating user: * Failed." as username | timeslice 1h | count _timeslice, username | transpose row _timeslice column username
